  <!-- EN: Wolfein Frag Grenade -->
  <W_Weapon_Grenade_FragGrenade.label>沃芬破片手雷</W_Weapon_Grenade_FragGrenade.label>
  <!-- EN: Fragmentation grenades. They can be thrown a short distance, where they'll explode, damaging anything and anyone nearby. -->
  <W_Weapon_Grenade_FragGrenade.description>破片手榴弹，可投掷至短距离目标区域并引爆，对周围的人员与物体造成伤害。</W_Weapon_Grenade_FragGrenade.description>
  <!-- EN: throw frag grenade -->
  <W_Weapon_Grenade_FragGrenade.verbs.throw_frag_grenade.label>投掷破片手雷</W_Weapon_Grenade_FragGrenade.verbs.throw_frag_grenade.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Gas Grenade -->
  <W_Weapon_Grenade_GasGrenade.label>沃芬毒气手雷</W_Weapon_Grenade_GasGrenade.label>
  <!-- EN: The gas grenades fielded by the resistance army can seep through most armor gaps, inflicting skin damage that is extremely difficult to heal. Although the resistance army claims that the gas causes no lasting effects and is primarily intended to disable MegaCorp’s precision equipment rather than personnel, the countless Wolfein civilians who continue to suffer agonizing pain and screams long after exposure would beg to differ. -->
  <W_Weapon_Grenade_GasGrenade.description>抵抗军列装的毒气手雷能够穿透大部分装甲的缝隙，对皮肤造成难以愈合的损伤。尽管抵抗军宣称这种毒气不会带来任何长期影响，其主要用途是摧毁军企的精密设备而非人员，但那些在事后依旧饱受剧痛折磨、惨叫不止的沃芬平民显然并不认同这一说法。</W_Weapon_Grenade_GasGrenade.description>
  <!-- EN: throw gas grenade -->
  <W_Weapon_Grenade_GasGrenade.verbs.throw_gas_grenade.label>投掷毒气手雷</W_Weapon_Grenade_GasGrenade.verbs.throw_gas_grenade.label>
  
</LanguageData>